                      words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#37r #66v #82r #83r" facs="039 069 084 085">folss. 37r, 66v, 82r, 83r, </locus>);
                      words of text are written interlinearly with a symbol (┬) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#35r" facs="037"> f. 35r, col. 2, line 3</locus>);
